<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Prompt:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <title>การจองสำเร็จ | ไชยปราการสัตวแพทย์</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #FF9AA2;
      --secondary-color: #FFB7B2;
      --success-color: #4CAF50;
      --light-bg: #F9F9F9;
      --text-color: #333;
      --border-radius: 12px;
      --box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Prompt', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF5F5, #FFF0EB);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
      color: var(--text-color);
    }
    
    .success-container {
      text-align: center;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
      max-width: 450px;
      width: 100%;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .success-container::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 8px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
    }
    
    .success-icon {
      font-size: 80px;
      color: var(--success-color);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation: bounce 1s ease infinite alternate;
    }
    
    h2 {
      color: var(--success-color);
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .success-message {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .booking-details {
      background: var(--light-bg);
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .detail-item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .detail-label {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #666;
    }
    
    .detail-value {
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .queue-number {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      margin: 20px 0;
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    
    .queue-number::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -5px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 80px;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
      border-radius: 3px;
    }
    
    .btn {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 30px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(255, 154, 162, 0.3);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(255, 154, 162, 0.4);
    }
    
    .btn i {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    
    @keyframes bounce {
      from { transform: translateY(0); }
      to { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .success-container {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      
      .success-icon {
        font-size: 60px;
      }
      
      h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      
      .queue-number {
        font-size: 40px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="success-container">
    <div class="success-icon">
      <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
    </div>
    <h2>การจองสำเร็จแล้ว!</h2>
    <p class="success-message">
      ขอบคุณที่ใช้บริการไชยปราการสัตวแพทย์<br>
      กรุณาตรวจสอบข้อมูลการจองด้านล่าง
    </p>
    
    <div class="booking-details">
      <div class="detail-item">
        <span class="detail-label">เลขที่การจอง:</span>
        <span class="detail-value">#<%= booking_id %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-item">
        <span class="detail-label">วันที่:</span>
        <span class="detail-value"><%= date %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-item">
        <span class="detail-label">เวลา:</span>
        <span class="detail-value"><%= time %></span>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="queue-number" id="queueNumber">
      #<%= booking_id %>
    </div>
    
    <button class="btn" onclick="goHome()">
      <i class="fas fa-home"></i> กลับหน้าแรก
    </button>
  </div>

  <script>
    function goHome() {
      window.location.href = "/users/main";
    }
    
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      setTimeout(() => {
        document.querySelector('.success-container').style.opacity = '1';
      }, 100);
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
